import React from 'react';
import { VStack, Box, Container, Text } from '@chakra-ui/react';
import { AddIcon } from '@chakra-ui/icons';

const LeftSideBar = () => {
  return (
    <Box width="100%" mx="2" my="2" >
      <VStack flex="1">
        <Box>
          <Container mt="5">
            <Text fontSize="18" color="white" margin="auto" as="b">
              List chat history
            </Text>
          </Container>
        </Box>
        <Box
          as="button"
          mt="auto"
          mb="6"
          bg="#545454"
          color="white"
          w="230px"
          h="40px"
          fontSize="16"
          borderRadius="20"
          align="center"
          justify="center"
        >
          Create new chat <AddIcon boxSize={'15px'} ml='10' alignItems='center'/>
        </Box>
      </VStack>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default LeftSideBar;
